<section id="about" class="relative px-6 py-16 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <p class="font-display text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-cyan-glow mb-4">About</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-8">
      Four disciplines, one way of working
    </h2>

    <div data-reveal class="space-y-5 text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm an Information Technology graduate and machine learning engineer based in Accra,
        Ghana, with hands-on experience gained through an internship at the Nigerian Army
        Cyber Warfare Command, where I supported cyber defence operations and network
        activity monitoring in a high-stakes, structured environment.
      </p>
      <p>
        My core work sits at the intersection of ML and full-stack engineering: I train and
        evaluate models, covering classification, transfer learning, and leakage-safe
        preprocessing, then take them the rest of the way, wrapping them in REST APIs
        (FastAPI, Flask, Django), containerizing with Docker, and shipping them through
        CI/CD pipelines that retrain, evaluate against the production baseline, and
        redeploy automatically.
      </p>
      <p>
        Design is not an afterthought bolted on at the end. I build brand identity, layout,
        and motion alongside the backend, because a model or a store is only as good as
        someone's ability to trust and use it. And outside of client work, I draw, using
        ink, ballpoint, and marker, which is where a lot of my eye for composition and
        detail comes from in the first place.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div data-reveal class="glass rounded-xl p-5">
        <p class="font-display font-semibold text-white mb-1">Education</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-200">B.Sc. Information Technology, Methodist University Ghana (2022–2026)</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-400 mt-1">Final Year Project: Smart Internship Placement and Tracking System (SIPTS)</p>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 100ms" class="glass rounded-xl p-5">
        <p class="font-display font-semibold text-white mb-1">Internship</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-200">Machine Learning Engineer, Future Tech Leaders Africa</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-400 mt-1">AI &amp; Machine Learning practical training program · May 2026 (ongoing)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
